 2010-02042010-02-23,  ,  ,  JUS, 
ActContraventions Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Application of Provincial Laws Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the APPLICATION OF PROVINCIAL LAWS REGULATIONS, in order to replace the title of a MANITOBA statute in Part IV of the Schedule to the Regulations by its new official title and create an equivalency between the expression "peace officer" used in the The Summary Convictions Act of that province and the expression "enforcement authority" in the Contraventions Act.
